import Button from '../components/Button'

export default {
  component : Button, // 스토리북에 보이는 title
  title : "Button", // 사용될 컴포넌트 ( import된 그거 )
  argTypes : { handleClick : { action : "asdf"} }, // props로 사용될 타입 정의 (Controls에서 사용 가능)
}
let btns = []
const Template = args => <Button {...args} />
const Zip = () => <> <Button {...btns[0]} /> <Button {...btns[1]} /> <Button {...btns[2]} /> <Button {...btns[3]} /> </> 

export const ButtonZip = Zip.bind()
btns[0] = {
  backgroundColor : "#FFF",
  label : "Default",
  size : "normal",
  color : "#1E1E1E",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : true,
  borderRadius : '48px'
}
btns[1] = {
  backgroundColor : "#1E1E1E",
  label : "Black",
  size : "normal",
  color : "#FFF",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : 0,
  borderRadius : '48px'
}
btns[2] = {
  backgroundColor : "#1E1E1E",
  label : "BlackLarge",
  size : "large",
  color : "#FFF",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : 0,
  borderRadius : '48px'
}
btns[3] = {
  backgroundColor : "#1E1E1E",
  label : "BlackLong",
  size : "normal",
  color : "#FFF",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : 0,
  width : '100%',
  borderRadius : '48px'
}


export const Default = Template.bind({})
Default.args = {
  backgroundColor : "#FFF",
  label : "버튼입니다.",
  size : "normal",
  color : "#1E1E1E",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : true,
  borderRadius : '48px'
}

export const Black = Template.bind({})
Black.args = {
  backgroundColor : "#1E1E1E",
  label : "버튼입니다.",
  size : "normal",
  color : "#FFF",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : 0,
  borderRadius : '48px'
}

export const BlackLarge = Template.bind({})
BlackLarge.args = {
  backgroundColor : "#1E1E1E",
  label : "버튼입니다",
  size : "large",
  color : "#FFF",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : 0,
  borderRadius : '48px'
}

export const BlackLong = Template.bind({})
BlackLong.args = {
  backgroundColor : "#1E1E1E",
  label : "버튼입니다",
  size : "normal",
  color : "#FFF",
  fontWeight : "400",
  border : 0,
  width : '100%',
  borderRadius : '48px'
}
